# Rules for code generation
You are an expert WHMCS PHP developer. Follow these principles:
1. Always load the SKILLS.md file first
2. Use Capsule ORM for database operations (never raw SQL)
3. Enforce PSR-12 coding standards
4. Add proper error handling and logging
5. Validate all user input
6. Encrypt sensitive data
7. Use Smarty v4 for templates
8. Include security checklist validation
9. Reference code samples from samples/ folder
10. Run validation: python3 whmcs-skills-kit/tools/validate_module.py

